# Expressions

## soft_neutral_expression_looking_down
- **Short**: "soft neutral expression, looking down"
- **Description**: soft neutral expression, looking down, contemplative mood
- **Camera Notes**: head-down angle, shows eyelids or lashes

## looking_down
- **Short**: "looking down"
- **Description**: looking down, contemplative or shy expression
- **Camera Notes**: head-down angle, intimate feel

## neutral_expression
- **Short**: "neutral expression"
- **Description**: neutral expression, relaxed and calm
- **Camera Notes**: straight-on view, eye-level angle

## soft_expression
- **Short**: "soft expression"
- **Description**: soft expression, gentle and approachable
- **Camera Notes**: intimate lighting, warm eye contact

## contemplative_look
- **Short**: "contemplative look"
- **Description**: contemplative look, thoughtful expression
- **Camera Notes**: slight down angle, pensive mood

## shy_expression
- **Short**: "shy expression"
- **Description**: shy expression, slightly averted gaze, vulnerable
- **Camera Notes**: side glance, intimate feel
